title: How Do You View it?
description:
Tony Kornheiser and Michael Wilbon discuss Aaron Judge’s 61st home run for the season and how we should look at it, if the Dolphins should get a pass on a short week and how the Mississippi welfare fund scandal makes Brett Favre look.
